            "title": "亞冠｜C朗拿度起孖迎40歲生日 領艾納斯贏波又創一里程碑",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/254d9d047626303bfb87c1af29c691eb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250204/_2025020412060479766.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周一亞冠精英盃B組，2日後(周三)踏入40歲的球星C朗拿度梅開二度，領軍主場4:0大炒艾華斯爾，同時收穫個人職業生涯第700場球會勝仗，為自己送上最佳的生日禮物。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f282cf4eb3911ca9cd4cbf41268baf28/2025-02/2025-02-03T180410Z_1456198623_UP1EL231E6XCU_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-AFCCHAMPIONS-NSR-WAS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fa0d7b0edb88bafe00e38567eec39050/2025-02/2025-02-03T184859Z_446041221_UP1EL231G9LD6_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-AFCCHAMPIONS-NSR-WAS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8cfa4a72c46333a92f08d38dcfd46e83/2025-02/2025-02-03T184958Z_832362836_UP1EL231GB8D7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-AFCCHAMPIONS-NSR-WAS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02c97cade610e20692cbd7464fea6641/2025-02/2025-02-03T190913Z_107217438_UP1EL231H7BDF_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-AFCCHAMPIONS-NSR-WAS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/47011313c6860cfbcbc11a496832ea9e/2025-02/2025-02-03T190924Z_2061146224_UP1EL231H7LDG_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-AFCCHAMPIONS-NSR-WAS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa5d8748f28908f110ee868e03bdb490/2025-02/2025-02-03T190933Z_1722631292_UP1EL231H7VDH_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-AFCCHAMPIONS-NSR-WAS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d3e66e00a556fcea8e0beb582be6346c/2025-02/2025-02-03T201618Z_1917534516_UP1EL231GHFD8_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-AFCCHAMPIONS-NSR-WAS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        C朗拿度梅開二度。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>艾納斯4:0艾華斯爾</h2>\n<p>艾納斯今場由艾夏辛遠射破網先開紀錄，之後C朗拿度射入12碼，以及接應傳中頂入完成梅二度，再加上艾法迪完場前埋齋，主場以4:0大炒艾華斯爾，助球隊提早鎖定亞冠精英盃16強席位。\n\n</p><h2>C朗拿度入2球慶生</h2>\n<p>葡萄牙球星C朗拿度將於2月5日踏入40歲，球隊主帥皮奧利賽前就曾直言：「送給C朗最好的禮物就是擊敗對手，尤其今場對己隊而言十分重要。」果然最終在隊友協助下，C朗梅開二度率隊取勝，為自己送上最佳的生日禮物。此外，今場更是C朗職業生涯的第700場球會勝仗，更添意義。\n\n</p><h2>新兵杜蘭表現麻麻</h2>\n<p>值得一提是，剛以7,700萬歐羅由阿士東維拉加盟艾納斯的射手祖漢杜蘭，今仗立即正選上陣。不過，其表現一般，全場僅26次觸球，3次射門都未能命中目標。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
